title: Problem in testscript
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Operating System

Windows

### DeepLabCut version

2.2.3

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

gpu

### Steps To Reproduce

You just need run examples/testscript.py
